data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $3000.00 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS. This is a beautiful Florida pool home with plenty of room to entertain in the large open yard, around the pool or in the open living area. The living area has new laminate floors throughout. The main bathroom has been updated. There is a lanai to enjoy when the sun is too hot. The newly refinished pool is perfect for entertainment. The screened encloser will help protect you from the Florida bugs. The pool deck has plenty of room to BBQ or just enjoy the sun. The oversized gate on the northeast corner of the lot gives you plenty of access to store your boat or any other toys you own. The large backyard is perfect for pets or anyone who loves the outdoors. The HVAC and ducts have been replaced in 2021.hot water heater replaced in 2019. The house has functioning rolldown hurricane shutters for safety during storm season. The house is located centrally between everything Pinellas and Pasco County have to offer. Shopping, gym, and many amenities located close to home. This area is highly sought after and this home will not last long.
